Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade  In a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:37.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:07.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:11.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:17.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:32.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The execution is tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:39.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard that, I was surprised, but…\Nstrangely enough I wasn’t sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:44.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It must be because of\Nthe dream I had last night…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:51.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That dream about\Nthe night I’ll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:02.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait here a moment.\NThe captain shall be arriving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:04.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:09.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m just an ordinary\Nnew squad member.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please address me\Nless formally?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… Yes! I’ll be careful in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:19.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:22.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know, from the Kuchiki clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:24.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! A new pet cat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:26.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she was exempt\Nfrom the graduation exam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:29.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as well as\Nthe squad entrance exam…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a pastime\Nfor the great nobles…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:35.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They’ve got to be kidding!\NWe’re here busting our butts…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the same here, after all …
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:42.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! What are you guys doing\Nloitering around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:46.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to your posts, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:51.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m the Lieutenant, Kaien Shiba!\NNice to meet ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Yes, sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Umm… Yes, sir…”?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with that greeting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:05.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your Lieutenant\Njust introduced himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:09.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re supposed to state your name and\Nsay, “Pleased to meet you too, sir,” right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s your name, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:14.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Ru…Rukia Kuchiki, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…? And...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pleased to meet you too, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:26.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An ordinary greeting,\Nan ordinary yelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:30.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,an ordinary subordinate-superior\Nrelationship…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:33.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome you to the Squad 13!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain isn’t\Nin the best of health,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so I’m pretty much\Nin charge of things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:43.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I wouldn’t mind if you sometimes\Ncall me “Captain Kaien” by mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:47.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I’ll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:54.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that ordinariness was, without doubt,\Njust what I was seeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:59.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, my squad entrance process\Nwas completed without incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:02.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What Seat are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:07.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah…well… My deepest apologies…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With my abilities, I’m afraid…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t get an officer’s seat\Nupon entry…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with the long face, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:26.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:30.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with you?\NEvery time you see me, you go “Eek!”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:32.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re going to hurt my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, here’s your share, drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:36.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes, sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:45.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, even if I asked\Nwhy you’re depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:48.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you probably wouldn’t tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:56.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you’re a member of this squad,\NI’m on your side no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You stink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You’re so cool, Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You stink! You stink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:07.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?\N“I’m on your side.” “On your side!”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta love him, huh?!\NGot him wrapped around your finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:10.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyone! Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:13.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You guys went off and got drunk again\Ndidn’t you, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:17.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki! Don’t let it bother you!\NI’m from Rukon District, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:21.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came here, there were those\Nwho gave me a hard time about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:23.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But for snot-heads like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you just have to\Nrub the snot right back at ‘em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Snot-heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch\Nof loudmouthed drunks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:35.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You guys need to\Ncome back to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:40.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien, you’re too rough sir, too rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:42.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You’re still on the clock, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don’t be a square!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I felt comfortable…being by Sir Kaien.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:02.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As always, Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:03.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our Lieutenant took it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-Ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Miyako…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:23.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, it’s nothing really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… That’s good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He—y!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He—y!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miyako,\NI didn’t know you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case\Nyou let the Hollow get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:41.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should come\Nto take care of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn’t get beaten that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:50.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki, sorry, but could you call\NSentaro and Kiyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’re pulling out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:52.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:56.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Miyako, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:00.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien had a wife…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:14.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Although a woman, she had risen\Nto the rank of the 3rd seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:18.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Despite being a woman warrior,\Nshe was intelligent, kind…and beautiful…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:24.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I admired her…\NI wanted to be like her…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She was my ideal…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:32.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:36.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Miyako received orders\Nfor a reconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we don’t know a thing\Nabout this Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:43.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,None of the Soul Reapers attacked by it\Nhas survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:51.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, I never thought\NI’d hear those words from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit kidding around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:01.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot forgive a Hollow\Nthat disturbs a soul’s peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:05.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As a Soul Reaper of the proud\NThirteen Court Guard Squads,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I must stop their evil deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Miyako…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:14.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry. It’s just a\Nreconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:18.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll leave the rest to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we’ll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:36.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:44.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki, any report\Nfrom the reconnaissance team yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No sir, they still have not returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It’s terrible!\NThe reconnaissance team!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:04.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She’s unconscious,\Nbut her life is not in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They’re all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All dead…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This sure is terrible…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:35.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The entire reconnaissance team’s dead,\Nexcept for Lady Miyako…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is Lady Miyako all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… They said\Nthat her life’s not in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that’s good…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:45.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She’s definitely someone\Nthat Squad 13 couldn’t do without.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:45.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:50.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? My, Lady Miyako,\Nshould you be up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What’s happening?! Lady Miyako…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:04.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:13.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,La…dy… Miyako…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:15.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What, what happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:16.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Miyako!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:57.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…\NShe couldn’t have gone very far yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kaien! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:03.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you chase her now, you’re doing exactly\Nwhat the enemy wants you to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It controlled Miyako,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:12.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and used her to kill off\Nthose subordinates who cared for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It sullied her pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:19.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go…Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:27.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Then I shall go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:33.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, you come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:38.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You two, take command of this place\Nand prepare the battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:40.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:41.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:50.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I smell them…\NThe smell…of those foolish prey…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:09.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:10.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:36.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien, I’ll go first\Nand check it out…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:41.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:43.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:00.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you are the first, eh?! Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:10.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How many Soul Reapers\Nhave you eaten so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder…how many…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:18.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don’t remember\Nthe count.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you regretted it…even once?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:27.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a silly question, boy.\NI too, like you, have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:31.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There isn’t a night that I don’t have regrets\Nafter eating a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I’m having regrets…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:36.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was just regretting\Nthat I should have used
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:40.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that woman Soul Reaper more\Nbefore consuming her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:44.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you controlled Miyako\Nand made her kill her comrades…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Controlled?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:51.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, not quite.\NAt that time, I was inside that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:55.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too bad…\Nthat I couldn’t show you the part
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:58.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,where I devoured that woman\Nto revert to this form…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:07.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come? Come!\NCome, come! I’ll eat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re fast! But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You touched me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:20.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rankle the seas and the skies!\NNejibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:24.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:31.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When someone touches my feelers,\Ntheir zanpaku-to vanishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:37.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s impossible!\NNever heard of such a power…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:39.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:45.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! But, why?!\NWe must help Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:49.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we help him,\Nwhat will become of his pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:55.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you help him now,\Nit will probably save his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:15:01.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, at the same time,\Nyou will surely be killing his pride forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:05.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about his pride?\NWhat’s pride compared to one’s life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:09.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, and remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:15.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are two types of battles, and\Nas long as we place ourselves in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:19.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we must always be aware\Nof the difference between the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:26.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Battles to protect lives and…\Nbattles to protect pride…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:32.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he is fighting for pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His subordinates’ pride…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His own pride…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:41.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And above all…\Nfor his beloved wife’s pride…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you going to ask\Nyour friends for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:04.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up…!\NI can handle you all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:11.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Then I shall do unto you\Nthe same as I did unto your beloved wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:16.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will control your body from within,\Nand against your will
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:20.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall slay your comrades!\NAmusing, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir…Kaien…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:45.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:48.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call me, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:57.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep calling my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:02.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that worried about me?\NAre you that much…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in love with me, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:12.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you love me that much…then…\NI shall eat you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Do you want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:29.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?\NWhy did this have to happen…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:32.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why…? Sir Kaien…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?\NWhy won’t you attack me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know why!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:45.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re thinking of a way to drag me\Nout of this body, aren’t you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:51.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am a spirit being, and he is a spirit being.\NNow our spirits are united.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:54.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can never be undone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…\NThen you leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall kill you\Nalong with Kaien’s body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:10.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Are you crazy?\NYou’re going to kill your own man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:10.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:16.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow the likes of you\Nto possess Kaien’s body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:21.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You won’t get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:39.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!\NWhy did you come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:43.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the time I came back,\NI didn’t even have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:14.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:18.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:21.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For letting me…fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:26.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir Kaien?\NDid you…intentionally…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:30.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia… I made you go along\Nwith my selfish request…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and put you through a horrible time…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that,\Nit must have been harsh…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:44.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you…\NI can leave my heart here…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:53.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… I haven’t done a single thing\Nto be thanked for…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:20:02.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The only person I saved was myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:09.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m detestable…\NI’m not worthy of being saved…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:15.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not worth\Nshedding blood over…ever…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:21.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:26.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s terrible! Rukia’s execution has…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:30.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:34.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:40.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The execution is tomorrow.\NIf that’s the decision, then I simply obey it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do not interrupt me\Nwith such needless talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:45.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:51.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Enough joking around!\NIt really is tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:54.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At tomorrow noon,\Nyour sister will be…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:02.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get so excited.\NYou’ll shorten your life, Ukitake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:06.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve already let\None of your men die before, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:16.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\Nshe is a member of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:21.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whether she dies or gets killed,\Nit’s none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:24.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to refrain\Nfrom any rash actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:33.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:37.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody stand up! Everybody fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:49.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Within your heart, you may feel uneasy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:53.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But keep your head right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:21:55.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:57.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:21:59.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:02.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me anytime! (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:04.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be here for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:08.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:12.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With a tough smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:16.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:20.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:21.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:24.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:26.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.73,0:22:28.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:36.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on following\NCaptain Ukitake anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:39.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not fair, Kotsubaki!\NI respect the captain too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:42.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I stalk the captain 24/7!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:46.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I always check the captain’s plans\Nand get there ahead of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that a crime?!